                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable H</hi> 11.) I took the prisoner and told him what he was charged with—he said, if I would go td the pawnbrokers he named, I should find the property—I went to five pawnbrokers—I found eight yards of it in all—the prisoner was in an empty room with four children, and not a morsel of food in the house.</p>
               <p>
